The bad part about this was that
people weren't always online

00:10:33.920 --> 00:10:36.020
and responsive right away.

00:10:36.020 --> 00:10:39.640
And I think we could of
made this not a problem,

00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:41.970
if we required everyone
in our project to download

00:10:41.970 --> 00:10:43.080
the mobile application.

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:44.970
That way, they would get
a notification immediately

00:10:44.970 --> 00:10:46.011
when they were mentioned.

00:10:46.011 --> 00:10:48.305
And they would be more
likely to respond quicker.

