Is there a reminder
of where they started?

00:26:04.440 --> 00:26:06.190
MATT: Yeah, it's on the castle.

00:26:06.190 --> 00:26:08.555
It's actually blocked
out right now,

00:26:08.555 --> 00:26:10.930
but toward the front of it.

00:26:10.930 --> 00:26:14.160
But there's a little
shadow there, an imprint.

00:26:21.910 --> 00:26:25.580
Because he ran out of candy
and then-- or actually, sorry,

00:26:25.580 --> 00:26:27.629
because he went to a
place that was underwater,

00:26:27.629 --> 00:26:30.170
he took too much damage and then
was swept away by the waves.

00:26:42.772 --> 00:26:44.230
And so on the
forecast, you can see

00:26:44.230 --> 00:26:48.090
that high water is coming
for quite a while, which

00:26:48.090 --> 00:26:49.720
is going to be a
danger for the toys,

00:26:49.720 --> 00:26:52.960
both in terms of possibly
getting swept away

00:26:52.960 --> 00:26:56.509
and not having enough candy for
all the toys that you're going

00:26:56.509 --> 00:26:57.800
to have to move out of the way.

00:26:57.800 --> 00:26:59.716
ANDREW: [INAUDIBLE] this time.

00:27:02.590 --> 00:27:05.925
NORMAN: Oh, he may
be out of luck.

