the symptoms of cholera

01:36:58.400 --> 01:37:00.510
and the importance
of early prevention

01:37:00.510 --> 01:37:02.620
and recognizing the
early signs of cholera

01:37:02.620 --> 01:37:05.210
to prevent the disease
from spreading.

